WEBVTT

1
00:17:31.330 --> 00:17:33.720 
我会这样回答你的问题
This is how I would answer your question,

2
00:17:33.720 --> 00:17:35.010 
曼奇尼先生
Mr. Mancini.

3
00:17:35.810 --> 00:17:37.330 
你怎么敢这样  先生
How dare you, sir?

4
00:17:38.240 --> 00:17:39.680 
你有私人生活吗
Do you have a personal life?

5
00:17:39.690 --> 00:17:40.810 
你有配偶吗
Do you have a spouse?

6
00:17:40.810 --> 00:17:42.560 
你知道把你的私人生活
Do you know what it would be like

7
00:17:42.560 --> 00:17:44.670 
像这样摆到台面上来说
to have your personal life spilled

8
00:17:44.670 --> 00:17:46.580 
会是什么样吗
across the stage like this?

9
00:17:46.690 --> 00:17:47.810 
被直播
Broadcasted

10
00:17:47.810 --> 00:17:50.390 
让你的朋友  同事
into the homes of your friends, your workmates,

11
00:17:50.390 --> 00:17:51.730 
你女儿的同学在家里都能看到
your daughter's friends at school?

12
00:17:51.730 --> 00:17:52.610 
你知道那会是怎样吗
Do you know what that would be like?

13
00:17:52.610 --> 00:17:53.670 
夫人  我只想报道
Ma'am, I'm only reporting...

14
00:17:53.670 --> 00:17:55.000 
如果我丈夫的不忠与我的工作
It would be one thing if my job

15
00:17:55.000 --> 00:17:57.280 
相关的话  那就另当别论了
had anything to do with my husband's infidelity.

16
00:17:57.280 --> 00:17:59.360 
我难以想象什么工作能跟那扯上关系
I'm not even sure what job that would be.

17
00:17:59.360 --> 00:18:02.170 
不过那样你的问题至少算是切题
But your question would at least then be pertinent.

